alsh |first1=Peter J. |title=Mrs. Mink Pulls Out of Presidential Race |url=https://www.newspapers.com/clip/48541069/honolulu-star-bulletin/ |accessdate=April 12, 2020 |date=May 24, 1972 |newspaper=[[The Honolulu Star-Bulletin]] |location=Honolulu, Hawaii |page=1 |via=[[Newspapers.com]]}}\n*{{cite web |ref=harv |last1=Woodruff |first1=Betsy |title=The 15 Women Who Have Responded to a State of the Union Address: Sadly, Many Were Remembered More for What They Wore than What They Said |url=http://www.slate.com/articles/news_and_politics/politics/2015/01/joni_ernst_will_be_the_16th_woman_to_respond_to_the_state_of_the_union_female.html |date=January 20, 2015 |magazine=[[Slate (magazine)|Slate]] |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20181117054758/https://slate.com/news-and-politics/2015/01/joni-ernst-will-be-the-16th-woman-to-respond-to-the-state-of-the-union-female-politicians-have-been-fighting-the-same-sexist-attacks-for-decades.html |archivedate=November 17, 2018 |publisher=The Slate Group |location=New York, New York |issn=1090-6584}}\n*{{cite news |ref=harv |last1=Young |first1=Samantha |title=Bush Signs Bill To Create Mink Post Office |url=https://www.newspapers.com/clip/47074063/hawaii-tribune-herald/ |accessdate=March 21, 2020 |agency=Stephens Washington Bureau |date=July 16, 2003 |newspaper=[[Hawaii Tribune Herald|The Hawaii Tribune Herald]] |location=Hilo, Hawaii |page=3 |via=[[Newspapers.com]]}}\n*{{cite book |ref=harv |last=Zhao |first=Xiaojian |title=Asian American Chronology: Chronologies of the American Mosaic |url=https://books.google.com/books?id=SQPRCA9S9WAC&pg=PA75 |year=2009 |publisher=[[ABC-CLIO]] |location=Santa Barbara, California |isbn=978-0-313-34875-4}}\n*{{cite news |ref={{harvid|''The Honolulu Advertiser''|2003b}}|author=<!--Staff writer(s); no by-line.-->|title=2 Students Each Receive $2,000 |url=https://www.newspapers.com/clip/47099164/2-students-each-receive-2000-13/ |accessdate=March 21, 2020 |date=October 13, 2003 |newspaper=[[The Hono